h your mail\r\nclient, please contact me.\r\n\r\nIf it's worth doing, it's worth over-doing.\r\n\r\n\r\n", 'subject': 'Re: PDF is blocked for printing, etc. OK for acroread (it behaves\r\n as expected), but KPDF allows me to print it, even if it is\tprotected! Why?'}